{"build_type":"executable","description":"Child worker for the as-completed fan-out. Reads g_fanout_shared, atomically claims its worker index (slot 0), reads n (slot 10+idx) and buffer (slot 20+idx), runs the proven cooperative scheduler (sum n) in its own buffer, writes result (slot 30+idx) and gettid (slot 40+idx). Then it records its COMPLETION RANK: pos = atomic fetch-add on the completion counter (byte address shared+16 = slot 2), and writes its own index into the completion-order ring at slot 60+pos -- so the ring lists worker indices in finish order. Finally sets done (slot 50+idx) last.","module_name":"worker-thread-recording-claimed-summation-completion-ranking","package_name":"worker-thread-recording-claimed-summation-completion-ranking","function_definitions":{"worker-thread-recording-claimed-summation-completion-ranking":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"one","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"sixteen","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":16},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"negone","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":-1},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"ten","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":10},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"twenty","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":20},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"thirty","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":30},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"forty","variable_type":"i64"